     1	---
     2	title: "PC-004 Python Regression Dataset"
     3	description: "Manual validation that scripts/skill_advisor_regression.py runs the checked-in P0 regression dataset to completion and reports pass/fail totals."
     4	trigger_phrases:
     5	  - "pc-004"
     6	  - "python regression suite"
     7	  - "regression harness coverage"
     8	  - "skill_advisor_regression.py"
     9	---
    10	
    11	# PC-004 Python Regression Dataset
    12	
    13	<!-- sk-doc-template: manual_testing_playbook -->
    14	
    15	---
    16	
    17	## 1. OVERVIEW
    18	
    19	Validate that `scripts/skill_advisor_regression.py` runs the P0 regression dataset at `scripts/fixtures/skill_advisor_regression_cases.jsonl` and reports pass/fail totals against the Python scorer.
    20	
    21	---
    22	
    23	## 2. SCENARIO CONTRACT
    24	
    25	- Repo root. Python 3 available.
    26	- MCP server built so the shim has a native option to delegate to where relevant.
    27	- Regression dataset present at the fixture path.
    28	
    29	---
    30	
    31	## 3. TEST EXECUTION
    32	
    33	1. Run the suite:
    34	
    35	```bash
    36	python3 .opencode/skills/system-skill-advisor/mcp_server/scripts/skill_advisor_regression.py \
    37	  --dataset .opencode/skills/system-skill-advisor/mcp_server/scripts/fixtures/skill_advisor_regression_cases.jsonl
    38	```
    39	
    40	2. Capture stdout and exit code.
    41	3. Inspect per-case results for any FAIL entry.
    42	4. Confirm the summary line reports the current dataset total and pass/fail counts.
    43	
    44	### Expected Signals
    45	
    46	- Exit code is 0.
    47	- Summary reports all cases passing for the checked-in dataset.
    48	- No case is marked SKIP without an explicit reason.
    49	- No prompt text is written to logs beyond what the dataset already contains.
    50	
    51	### Failure Modes
    52	
    53	| Symptom | Detection | Action |
    54	| --- | --- | --- |
    55	| Fewer than 52 cases | Dataset loaded partial | Verify JSONL integrity. |
    56	| Regressions reported | One or more cases FAIL | Triage per case. Block release until resolved. |
    57	| Non-zero exit but zero failures | Suite exits abnormally | Inspect runner and post-run hooks. |
    58	
    59	---
    60	
    61	## 4. SOURCE FILES
    62	
    63	- Scenario [PC-005](./005-bench-runner.md), bench runner.
    64	- Scenario [NC-003](../01--native-mcp-tools/003-native-validate-slices.md), native validate.
    65	- Feature [`08--python-compat/02-regression-suite.md`](../../feature_catalog/08--python-compat/02-regression-suite.md).
    66	- Source: `.opencode/skills/system-skill-advisor/mcp_server/scripts/skill_advisor_regression.py` and `scripts/fixtures/skill_advisor_regression_cases.jsonl`.
    67	
    68	---
